Enable or disable POP3, IMAP, SMTP AUTH in Office 365 

.DESCRIPTION
The script reads mailbox information going to a loop and disable legacy protocols (POP & IMAP & SMTP AUTH) for all users in Exchange Online. Automate the process via a menu and use a CSV (sample attached) to disable legacy protocols for specific users.

Disable Legacy Protocols in Office 365
Disable POP & IMAP Protocol for Bulk Mailboxes
Disable SMTP AUTH for all Mailboxes
Disable SMTP AUTH globally in your organization
Export SMTP AUTH for all mailboxes
Enable SMTP AUTH for multiple mailboxes (CSV)
Disable POP for multiple mailboxes (CSV)
Disable IMAP for multiple mailboxes (CSV)
Export Legacy Protocols (POP,IMAP,SMTP) information's
Exit Menu and logout from Menu
